Birds Of Prey (000 - 034) (2011 - 2014) (Digital) (Empire+DCP) 



Birds of Prey (Volume 3)

Written by: Duane Swierczynski (#1 - #17); Christy Marx (#18 - Present)

Drawn by: Jesus Saiz (#1 - 5, 7 - 8); Javier Pina (#6); Travel Foreman (#9 - 11); Cliff Richards (#12); Romano Molenaar (#0, #13 - 14, #16 - Present); Juan Jose Ryp (#15)

A "New 52" initiative book, starring a re-imagined Birds of Prey. With new writer Duane Swierczynski at the helm, the birds primarily consist of series mainstay Black Canary, and new character, Canary's college friend Starling. The team would later expand to feature Katana and Poison Ivy and Batgirl.
